&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Emergency Department / Urgent Treatment Centre - Receptionist - Band 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for shift work with a challenge, excellent learning opportunities, and no two days the same? Then come and join The Emergency Department Reception Team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Emergency Department and Urgent Care Centre has a busy 24 hour reception area, dealing with all patients arriving at the hospital via GP surgeries, Ambulance or self-referral. We currently have a receptionist vacancy for Part time hours. We offer a supportive environment within an enthusiastic and motivated team of receptionist and medical staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information regarding the above post then please contact: Harjinder Singh - Admin Manager: 01225 821855 or h.singh2@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
